rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0001
rows.name:
The only ones who seem to come
to me for money are the ones under
sorry circumstances.

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0002
rows.name: You saw for yourself, didn't you?

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0003
rows.name:
We're on the verge of war with Superbia and the people have to get
by on rations.

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0004
rows.name:
But the nobles in their ivory towers
are living as extravagantly as ever.

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0005
rows.name:
The mercenaries don't seem to have
it quite so bad either, as it's normal
for them to be hired as soldiers.

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0006
rows.name:
What I'm saying is that there's disparity
in the social classes.

rows.label: tlk43600142_01_msg0007
rows.name:
And I won't deny it, I'm just as
guilty of exploiting others for my
own benefit! Ha ha ha...
